findings.title: Out of gas
findings.description: The functions airDrops(), addRemoveFee() and blockUnblockAddress() may abort with OUT_OF_GAS exception if there is a long addresses list.

findings.title: Owner privileges (In the period when the owner is not renounced)
findings.description: The contract owner has excessive privileges during a certain period, including airdropping, changing fees, modifying wallets, distributing shares, marking addresses as bots, and adjusting transaction amounts.
